.DT
get_cfiles
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
get_cfiles

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
get_cfiles -  This method expands the wildcard based file name and turns it into a list of c files.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
string * get_cfiles(string str)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^str%^RESET%^ - the wildcard based file name
.EI

.SH Returns
.SI 5
the array of file names
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/global/player/path.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method expands the wildcard based file name and turns it
into a list of c files.  This automaticaly adds a .c to any
files.
.EP

